The paper discusses techniques for optimization problems in a wide range of applications, including matrix and tensor factorization and deep neural network training formulations. These topics are commonly studied in the computer science sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
